   Lock/write: [MarkerAppearance.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientObject/src/shared/appearance/MarkerAppearance.cpp:253)  
   Exact 36-byte format, but always locks 4 camera-facing vertices. Exclude.

5. `ShaderAppearance`  
